[{"id":"/sicpjs/3.2.2","tag":"TITLE","body":"3.2.2  \n    应用简单\n    \n      \n      函数"},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p1","child":[{"body":"\n    当我们在 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.1.5","href":"/sicpjs/1.1.5"},{"body":"节中介绍替换模型时，我们展示了如何通过\n    调用\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f(5)"},{"body":"\n    计算出136，给定如下\n    函数声明:","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":1,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHQCZMChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQBnARwIEMAnAUwAoAPASlADe2UCNAcyBVrW6gAVKG4BubAF98xctVp0CAWwD6VPPsYsOdHgBpQAT35DRY9hKn0mbLn1ABqN2a52ymqEpJQ0oHiczPbCouKS2nqGxqYeFsw+oACM1hnyGLxBuJEArIVAA","body":"function square(x) {\n    return x * x;\n}\nfunction sum_of_squares(x, y) {\n    return square(x) + square(y);\n}\nfunction f(a) {\n    return sum_of_squares(a + 1, a * 2);\n} "},{"body":"\n    我们可以使用环境模型来分析这个例子。\n    图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.4","href":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#fig-3.4"},{"body":"显示了通过计算\n    函数","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f"},{"body":"、","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"以及\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"sum_of_squares"},{"body":"\n    的定义在\n    程序\n    环境中创建的三个对象。每个\n    函数\n    对象都由一些代码和指向\n    程序\n    环境的指针组成。\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FIGURE","captionHref":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#fig-3.4","captionName":"Figure 3.4 ","captionBody":[{"body":"程序环境中的函数对象。","tag":"#text"}]}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p2","child":[{"body":"\n      <!-- 图已移动至后文以适应 SICP JS 分页  -->\n      <!-- 该图的代码在本文件后面的 PDF_ONLY 部分重复出现  -->\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FIGURE","captionHref":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#fig-3.5","captionName":"Figure 3.5 ","captionBody":[{"body":"\n\t    通过求值\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f(5)"},{"body":"\n\t    并使用图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.4","href":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#fig-3.4"},{"body":"中所示的函数创建的环境。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"\n\n    在图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.5","href":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#fig-3.5"},{"body":"\n    中，我们可以看到通过求值表达式\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f(5)"},{"body":".\n    所创建的环境结构。对 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f"},{"body":" 的调用创建了一个新的环境 E1，该环境以一个包含绑定了实参 5 的框架开始，其中 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a"},{"body":" 是 参数。 在 E1 中，我们求值 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f"},{"body":" 的函数体：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":2,"eval":false,"body":"return sum_of_squares(a + 1, a * 2);"},{"body":"为了求值\n    \n\t对于 return 语句，我们首先计算返回表达式的子表达式。\n      \n    第一个子表达式，\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"sum_of_squares"},{"body":",\n    的值是一个\n    函数\n    对象。（注意这个值是如何被找到的：我们首先在 E1 的第一个框架中查找，其中没有 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"sum_of_squares"},{"body":".\n    的绑定。然后，我们进入封闭的环境，即\n    程序\n    环境，在\n    \n\t图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.4","href":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#fig-3.4"},{"body":".)\n      \n    中找到该绑定。\n    另外两个子表达式通过应用基本运算 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"+"},{"body":" 和 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"*"},{"body":"\n    来计算两个组合\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a + 1"},{"body":"\n    和\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a * 2"},{"body":"\n    分别得到 6 和 10。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":"\n    现在我们应用函数\n    对象","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"sum_of_squares"},{"body":"\n    到实参6和10。这会产生一个新环境E2，在该环境中，\n    形式参数","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":"和","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"y"},{"body":"被绑定到这些实参上。在E2中，我们求值\n    \n\t      语句\n\t      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":3,"eval":false,"body":"return square(x) + square(y);"},{"body":"\n    这使得我们必须求值\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square(x)"},{"body":",\n    其中","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"是在\n    程序\n    框架中找到的，而","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":"的值为6。 再次，我们建立一个新环境E3，在该环境中","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":"被绑定为6，并在该环境中求值","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"的主体，即\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"return x * x;"},{"body":".\n    同时，在应用","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"sum_of_squares"},{"body":",\n      \n    的过程中，我们必须求值子表达式\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square(y)"},{"body":",\n    其中","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"y"},{"body":"的值为10。对","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"的第二次调用创建了另一个环境E4，在该环境中，\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":"，即\n    参数","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"的绑定，被设为10。在E4中，我们必须求值\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"return x * x;"},{"body":".","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p4","child":[{"body":"\n    需要注意的重要一点是，每次调用\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"\n    都会创建一个包含","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":"\n    的绑定的新环境。我们可以看到，不同的帧如何将所有名为\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":"\n    的局部变量分开。请注意，每个由\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"\n    创建的帧都指向\n    program\n    环境，因为这是由\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":"function\n    对象所指示的环境。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p5","child":[{"body":"\n    子表达式求值后，其结果被返回。由对 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"square"},{"body":" 的两次调用生成的值通过 \n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"sum_of_squares"},{"body":", \n      \n    相加，并且该结果由 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"f"},{"body":" 返回。由于我们在此的重点是环境结构，因此不详细讨论这些返回值如何在调用之间传递；然而，这也是求值过程中的一个重要方面，我们将在第 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"5","href":"/sicpjs/5"},{"body":"章中详细讨论.\n    ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 3.9","id":"#ex-3.9","child":[{"body":"\n    在 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.2.1","href":"/sicpjs/1.2.1"},{"body":"一节中，\n    我们使用替换模型来分析两种\n    函数\n    来计算\n    \n    阶乘，一个递归版本\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":4,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHQCZMChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8BDcqgJwvoBsAKIgSlAG9soYaGYBTMgWa1aAXnmgAjEJGqRAfiUq1qgFyhaAKjqMyLNl1oBaJTwDc2AL64GTVh04BWe0A","body":"function factorial(n) {\n    return n === 1\n           ? 1\n           : n * factorial(n - 1);\n} "},{"body":"\n    和一个迭代版本\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":5,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHQCZMChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8BDcqgJwvoBsAKIgSlAG9soYaGYBTMgWa0G5APoUyY5pwCMAGlAbQvANzYAvvmLlqMxmQVKVAB2ZUAJgXKaSVYtc0BbegA85bh58giKiElK0gUTWoAB8oD7+UWRCoWmgAPygdo7OKelpAFx0FlbKnMnKoABU2fZOLqCpBS3plcygANRams2t-Ql+Ae7RPPpG+BYsbFwArGNAA","body":"function factorial(n) {\n    return fact_iter(1, 1, n);\n}\nfunction fact_iter(product, counter, max_count) {\n    return counter > max_count\n           ? product\n           : fact_iter(counter * product, \n                       counter + 1, \n                       max_count);\n} "},{"body":"\n    展示使用每个版本的 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"factorial"},{"body":"函数\n    求值\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"factorial(6)"},{"body":"\n    时创建的环境结构。","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FOOTNOTE_REF","id":"#footnote-link-1","body":"1","href":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#footnote-1"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-1","count":1,"href":"/sicpjs/3.2.2#footnote-link-1","child":[{"body":"\n    环境模型不会阐明我们在 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.2.1","href":"/sicpjs/1.2.1"},{"body":"一节中提出的声明，\n    即解释器可以通过尾递归在常量空间内执行\n    函数\n    ——例如\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"fact_iter"},{"body":"。当我们在 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"5.4","href":"/sicpjs/5.4"},{"body":"一节中讨论解释器的控制结构时，\n    我们将讨论\n    \n    的内容。","tag":"#text"}]}]